      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-10-28T14:36:30Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>End Double Taxation of Successful Civil Claims Act </strong></p> <p>This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code to expand the deduction from gross income (above-the-line deduction) for attorney fees and court costs to include such fees and costs paid in connection with any legal action involving a civil claim (currently, limited to actions involving unlawful discrimination, the False Claims Act, and Medicare payments). </p>]]></text>
